{"name":"Brimgar of Doom","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Patron, Devil","alignment":"Lawful Evil","hitDice":"50","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":13,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"30","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":true,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"666","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"8","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"16","wisPoints":"18","chaPoints":"22","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"15","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"Due to the immense power bursting from the Chronolens, Brimgar must use all his legendary actions to maintain control over the artifact.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Chronolens","desc":"[MON] directly uses power from the Chronolens to control Time and Space. This starts with 8 charges (YotaWatts of power), and regains 1 per turn."},{"name":"Temporal Awareness","desc":"[MON] gains +10 to initiative."},{"name":"Legendary Resistance","desc":"If [MON] fails a saving throw, he can expend a charge to succeed instead."},{"name":"Time Dialation","desc":"Exerting control over the Chronolens takes a massive toll on [MON]. He loses his most powerful abilities and spell save DC. This becomes exponentially harder for [MON] as he continues to recklessly shatter time and space, and may cause him to become incapacitated. (YOU ARE NOT SUPPOSED TO DIRECTLY FIGHT BRIMGAR!!!)"},{"name":"Soul Tithes","desc":"When a creature has Stacks of Control, [MON] may expend those stacks to issue a general command (similar to the spell suggestion) involving their:\n\n1 Stack - Movement\n2 Stacks - Reaction \n3 Stacks - Bonus Action\n4 Stacks - Action"}],"actions":[{"name":"Lex Dominus","desc":"[MON] slashes with a fiendish sword that magically compels the soul to obey [MON]. [STR ATK + 1] to hit. _Hit:_ [STR 2D12 + 1] slashing damage. The target must make a **DC [CHA SAVE - 2]** Wisdom save or gain a Stack of Control."},{"name":"Impulsus Diabolo","desc":"[MON] channels his powers from the nine hells to compel a creature to obey him. If the creature fails a **DC [CHA SAVE - 6]** Wisdom save, it gains 4 temporary stacks of control that disappear at the end of the creature's turn."},{"name":"Time Stop","desc":"[MON] expends 4 charges to cast Time Stop so he can monologue without getting interrupted."},{"name":"Time Ravage","desc":"[MON] expends 4 charges and shatters the very fabric of reality. He can summon 3 Vanguards of his choice from before the Void fight. Once a Vanguard does, it can't be re-summoned again."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Heatwave","desc":"[MON] unleashes a heat wave that knocks back all creatures within a 5ft. radius prone if they fail a **DC [CHA SAVE - 2]** Con Save."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"deception","stat":"cha"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"fire","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"radiant","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"charmed"}],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Brimgar","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":4,"damage":[]}